test_odd_same_number:
assert [87] == [-11, -11]
  At index 0 diff: 87 != -11
  Right contains one more item: -11
  Full diff:
  - [-11, -11]
  + [87]
test_all_one_range:
assert [87] == [1, 1]
  At index 0 diff: 87 != 1
  Right contains one more item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1]
  + [87]
test_even_range:
assert [87] == []
  Left contains one more item: 87
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [87]
